<item>
            <title>[FLINK-8463] Remove unnecessary thread blocking in RestClient#submitRequest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8463</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;RestClient&lt;/tt&gt; unnecessarily blocks an IO executor thread when trying to open a connection to a remote destination. This can be improved by registering a &lt;tt&gt;ChannelFuture&lt;/tt&gt; listener which continues the execution once the connection has been established.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
